summary: fucking hell i'm so so angry right now... was looking at captain marvel trailers on instagram and was thoroughly enjoying them...
body:
fucking hell i’m so so angry right now… was looking at captain marvel trailers on instagram and was thoroughly enjoying them because i absolutely love carol danvers. then i made the unfortunate decision to look at the comments. fucking hell. the amount of butthurt little assholes who were bullying fans of the film and brie larson herself was unbelievable. they were calling anyone who dared to say they liked the film a feminazi and just being misogynistic pieces of shit. it’s fine to dislike a film. it’s not fine to attack anyone who likes it or attack the film for misogynistic reasons, racial reasons or any reason that hurts or discriminates against a group of people. if you do that then you’re honestly a piece of shit. get over yourselves. it’s 2019 for fucks sake. just fucking accept that women are allowed to be powerful. it doesn’t mean they hate men. it doesn’t mean that you’re having a feminist agenda forced on you. it just means that there’s a badass female superhero who a lot of people love. honestly just stop being such a piece of shit and get your head out of your ass.

radfems and anyone sexist towards either sex don’t you dare fucking interact
